# Assets folder for LearnLock app
# Required images:
# - icon.png (1024x1024) - App icon
# - splash.png (1284x2778) - Splash screen
# - adaptive-icon.png (1024x1024) - Android adaptive icon foreground
# - favicon.png (48x48) - Web favicon
# - notification-icon.png (96x96) - Notification icon

# Generate these using a tool like Figma, Canva, or use the following command:
# npx @expo/image-utils create-icons --input ./icon-source.png

# For development, you can use placeholder images from:
# https://via.placeholder.com/1024x1024/4F46E5/FFFFFF?text=LL
